) longer than wide, with marginal band and median area of radiating lines, surface smooth; setae sparse, needle-like, evenly scattered, without hair tufts. Mouthparts (Fig. 
4F
): chelicerae straight, anterior face unmodified; labium rounded, not fused to sternum, anterior margin not indented at middle; endites (Figs 
4G
, 
